---
title: Saucy Harissa Chickpea & Veggie Bowl with Herbed Garlic Dip & Tortilla Chips
description: When you simmer hearty chickpeas with subtly sweet veggies, garlicky tomatoes and our chermoula spice blend, the result
is pretty magical. Serve with a herby-garlic yoghurt for creaminess and of course oven-baked tortilla chips for crunch and
scooping!
